57</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1013/13/39/73/3/13397339thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>70</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>1966</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>##Overview
Riad Bleu Du Sud is a hotel located in the heart of Marrakech, Morocco. The 3 star property is close to the Dar Si Said museum and provides great accommodation for pleasure travelers. Among its amenities, it features: air conditioning, concierge facilities, internet access, 24-hour check-in and a TV lounge.

##Location
Due to its strategic location, the property offers great connections not only to various means of transport (airport) but also to the main attractions of the city such as: Maison de la Photographie, Ali Ben Youssef Madrasa, Assoufid Golf Club, Jardin Majorelle, Maison Tiskiwin and Ecomusee Berbere.

##Rooms
All rooms are comfortable, spacious and equipped with modern facilities such as: air conditioning, hairdryer, Wi-Fi connection and room service.

##Food &amp; drink
Depending on their preferences, the guests can choose between the hotel`s café and restaurant.  The Siham restaurant offers dishes from all around the world and a taste of the Moroccan cuisine.

